{
  "stem": "2906.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he let us go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this Turkestan he let us go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So if we came up, we were smiling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At least he let us go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what do we do now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have to-- something to-- so-- there was a Russian woman and I, we went to where they used to make shirts for soldiers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where were you at that point?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Turkestan.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Turkestan?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a train for the kolkhoz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't too long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Turkestan, was a lot people--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, prior to arriving in Turkestan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No on the train, only we four took the chance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when we came to Turkestan, there was a lot of, we used to call refugees.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we got there, first of all, I didn't have to eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the two women, two girls off and went to work in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took them in, and they needed hospitals, a lot of people, so they had a lot to eat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Russian woman and I, we went in this factory to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said we cannot give you anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Off in-- making shirts, sewing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, you cannot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have to stay at least a month till they'll ride you down to the city, then you can get some bread.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, we had no choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We worked with nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I had some money and I used to go in the market and buy, every day, half a pound, the-- the carrots.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, from a long time ago, I always had a little money that I didn't spend.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hold-- I hold it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I bought a half a pound carrots.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was living for a month with the carrots.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I looked like, I don't know, I was so skinny, bones.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
